    "synopsis": "On the fields of Velbayne, daemons spill out of every shadow and brotherhood is the only thing keeping the Rout alive. Packs of Space Wolves fight back to back — except for one. Bjorn, the warrior who has lost his entire pack, walks the line alone, sworn to a silence he will not break until he has put steel through the beast that killed them. As Leman Russ and the VIth Legion hold their ground, Bjorn hunts. A small, perfect grace note about grief, vengeance, and the particular loneliness of the Space Wolf who has outlived everyone he ever called brother.",
